segue_the_chain: The B-52’s are encouraging their friends to go to a party… Hank’s trying to get a particular friend to come to a party in the following song…

segue_dave.line: The B-52s started being a band in 1976, and so did The Jam...
segue_dave.explanation: The B-52s started being a band in 1976 and The Jam started being a band in the same year.
